    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Key Features</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-400 mb-10">
      <li>2 Bedrooms, 1 Bathroom</li>
      <li>Spacious living room with natural light</li>
      <li>Updated kitchen with appliances included</li>
      <li>Private off-street parking</li>
      <li>Pet-friendly (with approval)</li>
      <li>Washer/dryer hookup available</li>
    </ul>

